query:
UPDATE LocalStats
SET
  node_id = $2,
  TIME = $3,
  uptime_seconds = $4,
  channel_util = $5,
  air_util_tx = $6,
  num_packets_tx = $7,
  num_packets_rx = $8,
  num_packets_rx_bad = $9,
  num_online_nodes = $10,
  num_total_nodes = $11,
  num_rx_dupe = $12,
  num_tx_relay = $13,
  num_tx_relay_canceled = $14
WHERE
  msg_id = $1
